ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年高登貼呢條片 個個將鋒哥係神咁捧 笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間穀係生羊和鋒哥設局引水魚咋</blockquote><br />\n又靚仔做生意又老實</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實商人洗白白一條龍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「有料」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死，呢個世界真係多傻仔"},{"pid":"188e3ac2932d67a05b8488d99cd818bb2684f186","tid":499611,"uid":66365,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:49:23.000Z","msg":"樓豬酸撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fcc307986a8378d0eb88ea992bfa5bf2f2a7d2d","tid":499611,"uid":23618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:54:51.000Z","msg":"lemon由頭柒到尾<br />\n係而家搵到個錢咋唔代表有料"},{"pid":"84edcb03ae248a7a13ecafc4605a68f9c4517eff","tid":499611,"uid":736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lemon由頭柒到尾<br />\n係而家搵到個錢咋唔代表有料</blockquote><br />\n上面好多傻西話佢型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明廚神俾高登笑足十幾年<br />\n<br />\n希哥以前就真係好j喇"},{"pid":"6957d344e98e26fc9b6d8a876af6aae2f69451ec","tid":499611,"uid":77164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:07:12.000Z","msg":"柒極都靚仔過連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先唔講錢，靜無個樣都無得比"},{"pid":"2ebb53a58fa826a2f26167553d802bc8afb79bf2","tid":499611,"uid":77164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:08:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柒極都靚仔過連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先唔講錢，靜係個樣都無得比</blockquote>"}]}